import React, {Component} from 'react';

class New extends Component {
    render(){
        return (
            <form id="new-post">
                <input type="file" />
                <input 
                    type="text" 
                    name="author"
                    placeholder="Autor do post"
                />
                <input 
                    type="text" 
                    name="place"
                    placeholder="Local do post"
                />
                <input 
                    type="text" 
                    name="description"
                    placeholder="Descrição do post"
                />
                <input 
                    type="text" 
                    name="hashtags"
                    placeholder="Hashtags do post"
                />
                <button type="submit">Enviar</button>
            </form>
        );
    }
}

export default New;
